===================

Our goal is to achieve the following HTML rendering:

- the following example model 

```
abstract A
    b ?
    c -> C

abstract B
    d ?

abstract C : B

anA : A
    [ b ]
    [ c = aC ]

aC : C
    [ no d ]
```

